data.description: Welcome to 23 White Spruce Way! This beautiful 4 Bed, 2.5 Bath, 2 car garage home in the highly sought-after Poplar Preserve Subdivision is everything you have been looking for! Situated a short distance to shopping, schools, I-85, Piedmont Newnan hospital and more! This community features an oversized pool and playground area! Upon entrance of the home on the main level you'll find LVP flooring throughout the open concept living space! The kitchen features a large pantry, stone countertops, stainless steel appliances, ample cabinetry, center island and a huge eat-in area with access to the patio and large FLAT backyard. Heading over to the stairs, you cant help noticing the large living space featuring a warm and cozy switch operated gas fireplace! Just past the fireplace you'll find the stairs leading to the second floor, where all 3 oversized secondary bedrooms, laundry room, bathroom and the owner's suite are located! Each large room features walk-in closets! Bedroom 2 is extremely large, perfect to serve as a family den or shared bedroom for kids!. As previously stated this home is a short drive to EVERYTHING Newnan has to offer, truly move in ready and priced just right! No rental restrictions! Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity!!!
